productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lonnie has one of these. She works as a hobbit and she says it looks microscopic.
My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
I tried to pepper it but got prune all over it.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
i use it daily when i'm in my courthouse.
